      <title>anaconda学习笔记二 解决Mac终端jupyter command not found问题</title>
      <link href="/2019/05/13/anaconda%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0%E4%B9%8B%E4%BA%8C%20%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3Mac%E7%BB%88%E7%AB%AFjupyter%20command%20not%20found%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/"/>
      <url>/2019/05/13/anaconda%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0%E4%B9%8B%E4%BA%8C%20%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3Mac%E7%BB%88%E7%AB%AFjupyter%20command%20not%20found%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>因为Mac自带python是2.x版本，我用pip安装了python3.x，用jupyter notebook发现无法使用import pandas, matplotlib等等包，Google了很多，最后我的解决方式如下：</p><p>+– <strong>解决jupyter command not found:</strong></p><ul><li style="list-style: none"><input type="checkbox"> 安装python3:<code>pip3 install jupyter</code></li><li style="list-style: none"><input type="checkbox"> 在弹出的常常一串字的最后一段出现了我们juypter的安装位置<code>Requirement already satisfied: parso&gt;=0.3.0 in /Library/Frameworks/Python.framework/Versions/3.5/lib/python3.5/site-packages (from jedi&gt;=0.10-&gt;ipython&gt;=5.0.0-&gt;ipykernel-&gt;jupyter) (0.3.1)</code></li><li style="list-style: none"><input type="checkbox"> 在终端输入<code>jupyter notebook</code>提示command not found</li><li style="list-style: none"><input type="checkbox"> 接着输入<code>open .bash_profile</code></li><li style="list-style: none"><input type="checkbox"> 在弹出的文本编辑框中输入<code>export PATH=/Library/Frameworks/Python.framework/Versions/3.5/bin/:$PATH</code>输完后按command + s保存。注意：这里的路径需要和自己安装jupyter的位置一致，每个人安装的python版本不一致，所以需要注意查看jupyter安装位置，别输错了。</li><li style="list-style: none"><input type="checkbox"> 接着在终端输入<code>source .bash_profile</code>按回车</li><li style="list-style: none"><input type="checkbox"> 输入<code>jupyter notebook</code>弹出jupyter notebook网页，成功打开。</li></ul><p>+– <strong>解决jupyter notebook无法import pandas等包</strong></p><ul><li style="list-style: none"><input type="checkbox"> 在完成上述操作后，在notebook中输入<code>import pandas as pd</code><br><code>names1880 = pd.read_csv(&#39;name/yob1880.txt&#39;, names = [&#39;name&#39;, &#39;sex&#39;, &#39;births&#39;])</code>提示files not found，终于不是modules not found了。。</li><li style="list-style: none"><input type="checkbox"> 接着试着输入学习笔记一中基础点线图代码，没有报错。之前学习笔记一基础点线图代码我是在jupyter终端中输入的，这个demo可以完美运行，但是在notebook中提示modules not found。</li><li style="list-style: none"><input type="checkbox"> 我google了原因，可能是notebook的kernel与终端的kernel不一致，终端能运行，说明终端的kernel没问题，问题出在notebook的kernel上。然后我分别在notebook和jupyter 终端中中输入<code>import sys</code><br><code>sys.executable</code>两个运行结果不一致。</li></ul><p>+– <strong>jupyter command not found解决之后我又出了个新问题，在打开的jupyter notebook网页中，无法正常打开terminal，但notebook又是正常的。。。现在试着来解决两个kernel不一致的问题</strong></p><ul><li style="list-style: none"><input type="checkbox"> 首先在终端中输入<code>ipython kernelspec list</code>回车</li><li><p>[ ] 接着输入<code>open + 刚复制的路径</code>找到并打开kernel.json文件</p></li><li><p>[ ] 里面的内容是</p></li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line"> &quot;argv&quot;: [</span><br><span class="line">  &quot;需要替换的notebook kernel的路径&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">  &quot;-m&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">  &quot;ipykernel_launcher&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">  &quot;-f&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">  &quot;&#123;connection_file&#125;&quot;</span><br><span class="line"> ],</span><br><span class="line"> &quot;display_name&quot;: &quot;Python 3&quot;,</span><br><span class="line"> &quot;language&quot;: &quot;python&quot;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li style="list-style: none"><input type="checkbox"> 复制jupyter notebook terminal 中的kernel路径，把上面“需要替换的notebook kernel的路径”变为terminal kernel的路径。</li><li><p>[ ] 最后重新启动notebook，再次输入<code>import sys</code><br><code>sys.executable</code>检验notebook和其terminal的kernel路径是否一致。</p></li><li><p>[ ] 完成。</p></li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
